Compare 5 and 4, swap â†’ [1, 4, 5, 2, 8]
Compare 5 and 2, swap â†’ [1, 4, 2, 5, 8]
Compare 5 and 8, no swap â†’ [1, 4, 2, 5, 8]
Pass 2:
Compare 1 and 4, no swap â†’ [1, 4, 2, 5, 8]
Compare 4 and 2, swap â†’ [1, 2, 4, 5, 8]
Compare 4 and 5, no swap â†’ [1, 2, 4, 5, 8]
No swaps were needed in this pass, so the array is sorted.
